            <p>Teaching the Quran to kids in the USA can be challenging for Muslim parents, especially compared to Arab families who have access to more resources and Islamic environments. However, with the right approach, dedication, and support from institutions like <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a>, parents can successfully instill Quranic learning in their children.</p>
