                <p>Noorani Qaida is the foundation of Quran reading and pronunciation. Start by getting a Noorani Qaida book or using an interactive app recommended by <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a>. Their step-by-step methodology ensures kids grasp Arabic letters, sounds, and Tajweed rules from an early stage.</p>
                <p>Parents can also enroll in Noorani Qaida courses at <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a> to learn alongside their children, making home practice more effective.</p>
            </div>

