                <p>A simple routine could include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>20-30 minute daily sessions</li>
                    <li>Setting Quranic goals (e.g., learning one Ayah per day)</li>
                    <li>Reviewing progress weekly with a tutor from <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a></li>
                </ul>
