                <p>Quran apps make learning fun with engaging features. <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a> integrates modern technology into its lessons, offering interactive tools for effective learning. Some useful apps include:</p>
