                <p>Tajweed ensures proper pronunciation and respect for Quranic recitation. Parents should enroll their children in <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a>'s online Tajweed classes, where professional tutors break down the rules into easy-to-understand lessons.</p>
                <p>As the Quran states, <em>"And recite the Quran with measured recitation"</em> (Surah Al-Muzzammil, Ayah 4), proper Tajweed enhances a child's connection with the Quran. <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a>'s Tajweed courses are designed for kids, making learning simple and enjoyable.</p>
