                <p>Motivating children through positive reinforcement keeps them engaged. <a href="https://www.dararqam.com"><strong style="color: #800080; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Reem Kufi';">Dar Arqam</strong></a>'s learning system includes certificates and rewards for students who achieve milestones in their Quranic journey.</p>
